imary purpose is preventative maintenance: restoring your camera to reliable working order and ensuring consistent performance for years to come.<br\/><br\/><a href=\"\/blogs\/repairs-1\/cla-repairs-pricing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CLA & Repairs Pricing\">Please read about CLA's here<\/a><\/p>","page":""}},"topic_4giNHQ":{"type":"topic","settings":{"is_open":false,"title":"Pricing","text":"<p>All of our repairs are quote-based, but below are some examples of common repairs and past pricing. Please note that just because you are experiencing a similar issue, it does not guarantee the same price. Many factors — such as parts availability, the extent of damage, and model differences — determine the final cost.<br\/><br\/>See better breakdown <a href=\"\/blogs\/repairs-1\/cla-repairs-pricing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CLA & Repairs Pricing\">here<\/a><\/p><p><\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["topic_4QQKdG","topic_nHbVja","topic_WQ7DhW","topic_RFtHLb","topic_4giNHQ"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.accordions.name","settings":{"heading":"Your questions","heading_size":"h3","section_width":"max-w-narrower","color_scheme":"","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2"}}},"order":["main","repair_dDDKNX","callout_banner_g9cwFP","dual_tiles_6BEtMg","dual_tiles_9NcB6p","custom_liquid_YJJe3Q","multitile_c8qVhX","1754407872c586d4d7","accordions_QkyrzF"]}